WEBVTT

1
01:42:23.520 --> 01:42:25.000 
一面之词
Says you.

2
01:42:25.150 --> 01:42:25.930 
不
No.

3
01:42:26.320 --> 01:42:27.920 
他们能证明
Says them.

4
01:42:28.250 --> 01:42:30.260 
我们每个人的家园
Each of our worlds has been brutalized

5
01:42:30.320 --> 01:42:31.910 
都遭到了他们的蹂躏
by the Syndicates.

6
01:42:32.010 --> 01:42:35.030 
血红黎明会利用你们偷来的这批核芯素
Crimson Dawn will use their profits from the coaxium you stole

7
01:42:35.090 --> 01:42:37.250 
暴力统治更多星系
to tyrannize system after system

8
01:42:37.370 --> 01:42:39.230 
与帝国狼狈为奸
in league with the Empire.

9
01:42:39.460 --> 01:42:41.650 
那你会用它做什么
And what would you use it for?

10
01:42:42.260 --> 01:42:43.410 
像我妈妈一样
The same thing my mother

11
01:42:43.460 --> 01:42:46.470 
如果她还活着 戴着这副面具
would have used it for if she had survived and still wore the mask.

12
01:42:48.120 --> 01:42:49.500 
我会抗争到底
To fight back.

13
01:42:50.650 --> 01:42:52.510 
我们不是土匪
We're not marauders.

